  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the red snapper fillets under cold water and pat them dry with paper towels",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the minced garlic and grated ginger",
    "Add the soy sauce and sesame oil to the bowl and stir until well combined",
    "Place the red snapper fillets in the molcajete and brush the garlic-ginger sauce on top of each fillet",
    "Shape the cooked jasmine rice into small nigiri shapes and place on top of the red snapper fillets",
    "Garnish with thinly sliced scallions and toasted sesame seeds",
